    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age. The engine and transmission are functional, but you may notice some minor fluid seepage and a suspension that feels a bit loose on rougher roads. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and some fading paint, while the interior shows significant wear on the driver's seat and carpet. It is a solid, honest car for someone who needs dependable transportation and doesn't mind a bit of cosmetic and mechanical character.",
      "price": 18500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "fair",
